context:
KR:
&lt;란 이라는 자와 긴밀하게 메일을 주고받았다고도 했었지…&gt;
EN:
&lt;We were told she was in close relations with Ran, exchanging lots of messages...&gt;

KR:
&lt;운이 좋으면, 컴퓨터에서 미처 보내지 못한 메일 정도는 발견할 수도 있겠어.&gt;
EN:
&lt;If we're lucky, we might find a pending email or some other clue on her computer.&gt;

KR:
&lt;기술해방연합 이라는 곳이 뭘 하려는 곳인지 알 수도 있을 거야.&gt;
EN:
&lt;It should hopefully give us some insight into the technology liberation alliance, too.&gt;

KR:
&lt;의심 안 받고 언제나 얼굴에 포커페이스를 유지하는 수감자라면…&gt;
EN:
&lt;If I had to choose a Sinner who can keep a still face and avoid suspicion...&gt;

KR:
&lt;뫼르소! 할 수 있겠어?&gt;
EN:
&lt;Meursault! Think you can handle it?&gt;

KR:
&lt;응, 부탁할게.&gt;
EN:
&lt;Yeah, I'm counting on you.&gt;
